### Station aliases

This is the new alias-based configuration.

Each entry lets you define:

- a spoken alias
- the real Music Assistant station ID
- an optional display/station name

Example:

- alias: `rock antenna`
- station_id: `radio_browser://...`
- station_name: `Rock Antenne`

- alias: `bayern 3`
- station_id: `radio_browser://...`
- station_name: `Bayern 3`

If your command contains `{station_name}`, the blueprint will use this alias list instead of the fixed station.

